<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/24101087">如何证明幂剩余算法？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1822227" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="err">请证明此等式：</span>

<span class="n">x</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="n">a</span> <span class="n">mod</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="err">···</span><span class="p">((((((</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="n">mod</span> <span class="n">b</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">mod</span> <span class="n">b</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">mod</span> <span class="n">b</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="err">···</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">mod</span> <span class="n">b</span> 
<span class="err">说明：</span><span class="n">mod</span><span class="err">的意思是取余。（相当于</span><span class="n">c</span><span class="err">语言的</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="err">）</span>

<span class="err">也就是说，请证明</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="err">的</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="err">次方对</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="err">去余数的值，等于等式右边。。。</span>

<span class="n">PS</span><span class="err">：似乎是一种为了让计算机处理某种暗号时不数据溢出的解决方法。。</span>
</pre></div></div>


</div>
