<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$rixtox" href="/people/rixtox">Rix Tox</a>，<strong title="Cypherpunk" class="zu-question-my-bio">Cypherpunk</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="1">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$huzhi-zhang" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/huzhi-zhang" class="zg-link" title="huzhi zhang">huzhi zhang</a></span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1822227" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">这是RSA中用到的快速求模算法，叫作<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Modular_exponentiation" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Modular exponentiation<i class="icon-external"></i></a>。<br><br>如果要从数学角度证明这个等式，我们只需要证明一个定理：<br><blockquote>如果<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%5Ek+%5Cequiv+r_k+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29%2C+k+%5Cin+%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D" alt="x^k \equiv r_k \;(\bmod\; n), k \in \mathbb{N}" eeimg="1">，那么可以得到<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%5E%7Bk%2B1%7D+%5Cequiv+x+%5Ccdot+r_k+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29" alt="x^{k+1} \equiv x \cdot r_k \;(\bmod\; n)" eeimg="1">。</blockquote>这个定理非常容易证明：<br><img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbecause+x%5Ek+%5Cequiv+r_k+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29%2C+k+%5Cin+%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D+%5C%5C%0A%5Ctherefore+x%5Ek+%3D+q%5Ccdot+n+%2B+r_k%2C+q+%5Cin+%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D+%5C%5C%0A+x%5E%7Bk%2B1%7D+%3D+q%5Ccdot+n+%5Ccdot+x+%2B+x+%5Ccdot+r_k+%5C%5C%0A%5Ctherefore+x%5E%7Bk%2B1%7D+%5Cequiv+%5Cfrac%7Bq%5Ccdot+n+%5Ccdot+x+%2B+x+%5Ccdot+r_k%7D%7Bn%7D+%5Cequiv+x+%5Ccdot+r_k+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29" alt="\because x^k \equiv r_k \;(\bmod\; n), k \in \mathbb{N} \\
\therefore x^k = q\cdot n + r_k, q \in \mathbb{N} \\
 x^{k+1} = q\cdot n \cdot x + x \cdot r_k \\
\therefore x^{k+1} \equiv \frac{q\cdot n \cdot x + x \cdot r_k}{n} \equiv x \cdot r_k \;(\bmod\; n)" eeimg="1"><br><br>其实这样就已经可以直接得到结论了，不过为了解释得更清楚，我再进一步说明一下Modular Exponentiation的原理。<br>如果我们要求一个值<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=r" alt="r" eeimg="1">使得<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%5Ee+%5Cequiv+r+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29" alt="x^e \equiv r \;(\bmod\; n)" eeimg="1">，我们先求<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=r_1" alt="r_1" eeimg="1">使得<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%5E1+%5Cequiv+r_1+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29" alt="x^1 \equiv r_1 \;(\bmod\; n)" eeimg="1">，也就是代码中的<br><div class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-text">(x mod n)
</code></pre></div>然后根据我们证明的定理，<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=x+%5Ccdot+r_1" alt="x \cdot r_1" eeimg="1">满足<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%5E%7B1%2B1%7D+%5Cequiv+x%5E2+%5Cequiv+r_2+%5Cequiv+x+%5Ccdot+r_1+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29" alt="x^{1+1} \equiv x^2 \equiv r_2 \equiv x \cdot r_1 \;(\bmod\; n)" eeimg="1">，但它不是最小的同余数，所以我们还要对它求余，也就是代码中的<br><div class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-text">((x mod n)*x) mod n)
</code></pre></div>这样得到的数就可以作为最小的模<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=r_2" alt="r_2" eeimg="1">，然后一路递归上去：<br><img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbegin%7Balign%7D%0Ar_2+%5Ccdot+x+%26%5Cequiv+r_3+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29+%5C%5C%0Ar_3+%5Ccdot+x+%26%5Cequiv+r_4+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29+%5C%5C%0A...+%26%5Cequiv+...+%5C%5C%0Ar_%7Be-1%7D+%5Ccdot+x+%26%5Cequiv+r_e+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29+%5C%5C%0A%5Cend%7Balign%7D" alt="\begin{align}
r_2 \cdot x &amp;\equiv r_3 \;(\bmod\; n) \\
r_3 \cdot x &amp;\equiv r_4 \;(\bmod\; n) \\
... &amp;\equiv ... \\
r_{e-1} \cdot x &amp;\equiv r_e \;(\bmod\; n) \\
\end{align}" eeimg="1"><br>最终我们就能得到最小的<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=r_e" alt="r_e" eeimg="1">使得<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%5Ee+%5Cequiv+r_e+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29" alt="x^e \equiv r_e \;(\bmod\; n)" eeimg="1">，也就是你给出的递归扩展，写成迭代应该是这个样子的：<br><div class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-coffee-script"><span class="nv">modPow = </span><span class="nf">(base, exponent, modulus) -&gt;</span>
  <span class="nv">r = </span><span class="mi">1</span>
  <span class="k">for</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">..</span><span class="nx">exponent</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="nv">r = </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">r</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="nx">base</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="nx">modulus</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="nx">r</span>
</code></pre></div>如果用递归反而不如迭代的方便：<br><div class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-haskell"><span class="nf">powm</span> <span class="ow">::</span> <span class="kt">Integer</span> <span class="ow">-&gt;</span> <span class="kt">Integer</span> <span class="ow">-&gt;</span> <span class="kt">Integer</span> <span class="ow">-&gt;</span> <span class="kt">Integer</span> <span class="ow">-&gt;</span> <span class="kt">Integer</span>
<span class="nf">powm</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="n">m</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="ow">=</span> <span class="n">r</span>
<span class="nf">powm</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="n">m</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">|</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="p">`</span><span class="n">mod</span><span class="p">`</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="ow">=</span> <span class="n">powm</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="p">`</span><span class="n">mod</span><span class="p">`</span> <span class="n">m</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span> <span class="p">`</span><span class="n">div</span><span class="p">`</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">m</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="p">`</span><span class="n">mod</span><span class="p">`</span> <span class="n">m</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nf">powm</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="n">m</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="ow">=</span> <span class="n">powm</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="p">`</span><span class="n">mod</span><span class="p">`</span> <span class="n">m</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span> <span class="p">`</span><span class="n">div</span><span class="p">`</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">m</span> <span class="n">r</span>
</code></pre></div>顺便提一下这个算法的效率仅跟<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%5Ee+%5Cequiv+r+%5C%3B%28%5Cbmod%5C%3B+n%29" alt="x^e \equiv r \;(\bmod\; n)" eeimg="1">中的<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=e" alt="e" eeimg="1">有关，为<img src="http://zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cmathcal%7BO%7D%28%5Clog%7Be%7D%29" alt="\mathcal{O}(\log{e})" eeimg="1">。
<a href="/question/24101087/answer/26704397" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
